front.title: Bothan Spy
front.gametext: May be targeted (instead of a droid) by Death Star Plans. When targeted by Death Star Plans, makes that Effect immune to Alter and adds one destiny to Force retrieved with Death Star Plans. May not be targeted by Nabrun Leids.
front.lore: Bothans operate the most complex spy network in the galaxy. Discovered the location of the second Death Star. Ambitious. Resourceful. Furry. Tend to die in large numbers.

pulledBy: Soth Petikkin (when at a Jabba's Palace site you control)
